com.amazonaws.services.dynamodbv2.datamodeling
Class S3Link.ID

java.lang.Object
  com.amazonaws.services.dynamodbv2.datamodeling.S3Link.ID
Enclosing class:
S3Link
public static class S3Link.ID
extends java.lang.Object

JSON wrapper of an S3Link identifier, which consists of the S3 region id, bucket name and key. Sample JSON serialized form: 

 {"s3":{"bucket":"mybucket","key":"mykey","region":"us-west-2"}}
 {"s3":{"bucket":"mybucket","key":"mykey","region":null}}
Note for S3 a null region means US standard.

See Also:
Region.US_Standard
